Only authorized Excelicare employees or agents carrying out permitted business functions are permitted to access Personal Information.

Excelicare may receive Personal Information from registered users of our solutions as part of our provision of services to and on behalf of users.
Such information may only be used by Excelicare as is reasonably necessary to perform obligations as contracted by users.
This document details how Excelicare stores, uses, and collects Personal Information provided by registered users about patients.
